metadata.name: Hope
metadata.description:
I took this picture after losing my home. At my lowest point, a Marine reached out to me and encouraged me to seek help. I learned I was suffering from PTSD. I call this photo "Hope."

I hope to bring my photography to NFTs throughout my life.

Part of the "Hope" Collection by Brendan S Bigney (The Nuclear Cowboy), Marine Corps Veteran, photographer, and Multi-Award-Winning Author.
